  <bioghist id="aspace_61f9fd712a60bbba15965ab83c833584">
    <head>ORGANIZATIONAL HISTORY</head>
<p>The Class Notes are a co-ed a cappella group founded in 1983 that performs a varied repertoire of contemporary Pop, R&amp;B, Rock and Hip-hop songs.</p>  </bioghist>
  <scopecontent id="aspace_c38ebc04d116f30144648b9e803972d8">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Music, photos, CDs, videos, sheet music arrangements, membership lists, history and files relating to the administration and performances of the Class Notes.</p>  </scopecontent>
